INSERT INTO `liquors` VALUES (1,'감홍로 백자(Gamhongro Baekja)','400ml 700ml',40.0,3.0,'Rice (70%) meso (30%) longan meat dermis ginger cloves licorice ground vinegar','The first taste is sweet and it smells like herbal medicine with cinnamon ginger licorice and longan meat. Although the alcohol content is 40 degrees the mouthfeel is soft with the fragrance of cinnamon as the main ingredient and the subtle sweetness.','쌀','','','','','','','','https://img3.daumcdn.net/thumb/R658x0.q70/?fname=https://t1.daumcdn.net/news/202105/25/dailylife/20210525052118095dbtl.png',13,6),(2,'삼해소주(Samhae Soju)','400ml',45.0,4.0,'Non-glutinous rice glutinous rice koji','Seoul Intangible Cultural Heritage No. 8. The representative distilled soju of Samhae Soju which has been designated as a traditional food master by the Ministry of Agriculture Food and Rural Affairs.','쌀','','누룩','','','','','','https://assets.business.veluga.kr/media/public/%E1%84%89%E1%85%A1%E1%86%B7%E1%84%92%E1%85%A2%E1%84%89%E1%85%A9%E1%84%8C%E1%85%AE_%E1%84%89%E1%85%A1%E1%86%B7%E1%84%92%E1%85%A2%E1%84%89%E1%85%A9%E1%84%8C%E1%85%AE.png',13,4),(3,'서울의 밤(Night of Seoul)','375ml',25.0,3.0,'Plum distilled liquor honey glucose juniper fruit purified water','Purified by low-temperature secondary distillation and freezing filtration technology','','정제수','','','','','','','https://contents.sixshop.com/uploadedFiles/101447/product/image_1564727925900.jpg',13,5),(4,'동백꽃, 제주(Camellia flower jeju)','365ml',16.0,4.0,'Camellia petals, purified water, glucose yeast','\nRed Camellia Petal Tea is known not only for its umami taste but also for its beautiful color. It is made with pure water from Gosan-ri, Hangyeong-myeon, Jeju City, healthy camellia petals from Jeju, and red yeast produced in the brewery itself, without chemical dyes.','','정제수','','효모','','','동백꽃잎','','https://assets.business.veluga.kr/media/public/%EB%8F%99%EB%B0%B1%EA%BD%83_%EC%A0%9C%EC%A3%BC.png',16,3),(5,'오희 스파클링 막걸리(Ohee Sparkling Rice Wine)','500ml',8.5,5.0,'White rice dried omija coenzyme yeast purified water','With its attractive pink color it is well received by young people and women and it is a popular Mungyeong Saejae hit product favored by tourists visiting Mungyeong Saejae.','쌀','정제수','','효모','','','','','https://assets.business.veluga.kr/media/public/%E1%84%8B%E1%85%A9%E1%84%92%E1%85%B4_%E1%84%89%E1%85%B3%E1%84%91%E1%85%A1%E1%84%8F%E1%85%B3%E1%86%AF%E1%84%85%E1%85%B5%E1%86%BC_%E1%84%86%E1%85%A1%E1%86%A8%E1%84%80%E1%85%A5%E1%86%AF%E1%84%85%E1%85%B5.png',16,3),(6,'유자향주(Citron Flavor Liquor)','750ml',6.0,5.0,'Rice (domestic) citron (from Goheung) aspartame','‘Cyuja Hyangju’ of the Clean Farming Association is the representative specialty of Goheung-gun which accounts for more than 35% of the nation’s citron production.','쌀','','','','','','','','https://i0.wp.com/www.sulsulsul.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/%EC%9C%A0%EC%9E%90%ED%96%A5%EC%A3%BC.jpg?fit=510%2C510&ssl=1',12,2),(7,'백년향 (Baek Nyun Hyang)','500ml',10.0,5.0,'Rice yeast purified water','This is a Samyangju-style takju (makgeolli) in which the first base is brewed and the second is added and then soaked for a total of three times. It is made from yeast made from Yeoju rice in Gyeonggi-do and Korean wheat native to Korea.','쌀','정제수','누룩','','','','','','http://img.danawa.com/prod_img/500000/782/748/img/11748782_1.jpg?shrink=500:500&_v=20200707134829',16,8),(8,'맑은내일 발효 막걸리(Margeun Naeil Fermented Makeoli)','750ml',7.0,4.5,'Purified water rice yeast purified enzyme aspartame','A delicate acidity and a deep soft fragrance.Makgeolli made with brewing technology that started as a rice mill and has been around for over 70 years. The combination of sweet and sour taste created by abundant lactic acid bacteria is good with oily foods.','쌀','정제수','','','','','','','https://assets.business.veluga.kr/media/public/%E1%84%86%E1%85%A1%E1%86%B0%E1%84%8B%E1%85%B3%E1%86%AB_%E1%84%82%E1%85%A2%E1%84%8B%E1%85%B5%E1%86%AF_%E1%84%87%E1%85%A1%E1%86%AF%E1%84%92%E1%85%AD_%E1%84%86%E1%85%A1%E1%86%A8%E1%84%80%E1%85%A5%E1%86%AF%E1%84%85%E1%85%B5.png',16,3),(9,'영탁막걸리(Yeongtak Makeoli)','750ml',6.0,5.0,'Purified water polished rice (domestic production) entry (rice wheat) starch syrup oligosaccharide yeast (wheat) yeast aspartame acesulfalpotassium','Trot singer Young-tak and singer Kang-jin\'s song \"A glass of makgeolli\"\" was a big hit and was released on May 13 2020 to coincide with Young-tak\'s birthday.\"','쌀','정제수','누룩','효모','','','','','https://img.hankyung.com/photo/202105/01.26373630.1.jpg',16,3),(10,'바나나 주(Bannana Falvor Liquor)','750ml',4.0,4.5,'Rice soup purified water banana concentrate prepared broth yeast starch syrup','The sweet and fragrant smell of bananas makes you feel like you are drinking banana milk. It is made with domestic rice and has a low alcohol content of 4% making it a drink that young people will especially like.','쌀','정제수','','효모','','','과당','','https://assets.business.veluga.kr/media/public/%E1%84%89%E1%85%A6%E1%84%8C%E1%85%A9%E1%86%BC_%E1%84%87%E1%85%A1%E1%84%82%E1%85%A1%E1%84%82%E1%85%A1%E1%84%8C%E1%85%AE_hCNMT8a.png',15,4),(11,'백운 복분자 와인 (Baekun Bokbunja Wine)','360ml',11.0,4.5,'Rice native bokbunja juice','The sweet and fragrant taste of bokbunja. It goes well with grilled eel. I think it would be good to try it with Gochang’s specialty Pungcheon eel.','쌀','','','','','','과당','','https://i1.wp.com/www.sulsulsul.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/%EB%B0%B1%EC%9A%B4-%EB%B3%B5%EB%B6%84%EC%9E%90%EC%99%80%EC%9D%B8.jpg?fit=830%2C830&ssl=1',16,9),(12,'메로니아(Melonia)','750ml',4.0,4.0,'Rice soup yeast lactic acid melon flavor starch syrup etc.','Melonia is a drink that seems to have melon-flavored ice cream melted in makgeolli with the unique sweetness of melon.','쌀','정제수','','효모','','','과당','','http://img.danawa.com/prod_img/500000/173/730/img/11730173_1.jpg?shrink=500:500&_v=20200703152626',16,1),(13,'르깔롱(Leccalon)','500ml',16.0,4.5,'Purified water alcohol high fructose tabasheer melon flavor ragi lime coconut flavor Wilton Sky Icing Color','This liquor is a traditional liquor made from Korean rice and yeast with the main ingredient \'Jakhyeol\' extracted by heating bamboo for a long time. Coconuts and melons are added here to clearly reveal the fruity flavor.','쌀','','','','','','과당','','https://assets.business.veluga.kr/media/public/%E1%84%85%E1%85%B3%E1%84%81%E1%85%A1%E1%86%AF%E1%84%85%E1%85%A9%E1%86%BC.png',15,8),(14,'동강더덕주(Dong Gang Deodeokju)','360ml',20.0,4.0,'Deodeok Jujube Giza Licorice Wonji','Donggang deodeokju is a local specialty in Yeongwol Gangwon-do made with deodeok harvested from the blessed region of Gangwon-do as a raw material and supplemented with jujube omija and licorice which are good for the body for 100 days.','','','','','','','','','https://i1.wp.com/www.sulsulsul.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/%EB%8F%99%EA%B0%95%EB%8D%94%EB%8D%95%EC%A3%BC.jpg?fit=800%2C800&ssl=1',13,2),(16,'제주몬순커피주(Jeju Monsun Coffee Flavor Liquor)','200ml',11.0,5.0,'Purified water sugar green coffee beans yeast','It is light and has a refreshing acidity that clears the mouth so it goes well with light foods such as fish dishes steamed ribs japchae and sujebi.','','정제수','','효모','','','과당','설탕','https://sooldamhwa-static-files.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/content_images/contents_images-1630318575694-jj+ms+coffe1.jpg',14,8),(17,'금과 명주(Keum and Myeongju)','750ml',40.0,4.5,'Apple Distilled Wine High Fructose Apple Flavor Caramel','The apple wine brewing method unique to Appliz Korea developed after 15 years of research and aging in an earthenware jar suitable for traditional Korean wines.','','정제수','','','','주정','','설탕','https://betterb.co.kr/market/upload_files/prd_img/201812/15444072698.jpg',12,4),(18,'꿀샘 16 (Kkul Sam 16)','375ml',16.0,4.0,'Purified water alcohol sugar natural honey ginger citric acid','A refreshing drink with a hint of lemon and sweet honey. It has a flavor as sweet as the scent and you can feel a slight burning sensation and a bitter aftertaste. Highly recommended for those who like fruit soju or want a light drink!','','정제수','','','','주정','','','https://view01.wemep.co.kr/wmp-product/0/128/1182101280/pm_uicthzzlt77h.jpg?1595298033',13,6),(19,'진쾌남 (Jin Que Nam)','330ml',40.0,4.0,'Domestic rice chestnut yeast goji berry omija cornflower oil sagebrush cordyceps cordyceps purified water','Jinkwae Namju is a representative drink for men who admire the taste and aroma of omija cornflower oil sagebrush goji berries cordyceps tosaja and honey on the night of Gongju.','쌀 ','정제수','누룩','','','','','','https://assets.business.veluga.kr/media/public/%E1%84%89%E1%85%A1%E1%84%80%E1%85%A9%E1%86%A8%E1%84%8B%E1%85%A3%E1%86%BC%E1%84%8C%E1%85%A9%E1%84%8B%E1%85%AF%E1%86%AB_%E1%84%8F%E1%85%AB%E1%84%82%E1%85%A1%E1%86%B7_40_330.png',13,2),(20,'한비 무병장수술(Hanbi Mubyungjang Soo Liquor)','375ml 750ml',35.0,4.0,'Domestic rice black ginseng ginseng ginseng omija goji berry bokbunja psyllium tosaja cornflower oil','Herbal medicine without disease is a traditional method of fermenting rice and then distilling grain wine with black ginseng ginseng spiny ginseng white sorghum omija gugija bokbunja psyllium tosaja and cornus soybeans which are blended with medicinal herbs that are good for health. It is a functional alcohol that helps.','쌀','','누룩','','','','','','https://i1.wp.com/www.sulsulsul.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/%EB%AC%B4%EB%B3%91%EC%9E%A5%EC%88%98%EC%88%A0375.jpg?fit=900%2C900&ssl=1',14,4),(21,'한비 동충하초술(Hanbi Dongchung Hajo Liquor)','375ml 750ml',35.0,4.0,'Domestic rice yeast spiny hornwort root cordyceps cordyceps purified water','Hanbi Cordyceps Cordyceps Sake is made by fermenting rice with traditional techniques and then adding Militaris Cordyceps Cordyceps Licorice and Orchids to the distilled grain wine to enjoy a mild and gentle fragrance. In particular the cordycepin component of cordyceps increases immunity and helps blood circulation.','쌀','정제수','누룩','','','','','','http://image.enuri.info/webimage_300/2827500000/2827560000/2827566185.jpg',13,4),(22,'과하주23(Gwahaju 23)','400ml 700ml 1000ml',23.0,4.0,'100% rice','Gwangju is a traditional Korean fortified makgeolli. Refined rice wine Cheongju is fortified by adding soju shochu to produce gwaha-gwangju.','쌀','','','','','','','','http://img.danawa.com/prod_img/500000/553/290/img/5290553_1.jpg?shrink=500:500&_v=20180831171228',13,3),(23,'매아랑(Maeharang)','750ml',10.7,5.0,'domestic plum','Developed the world\'s first Hadong special liquor made from plums. High-quality Mae-arang made from our fruits is rich in minerals and has a clean wine taste.','','','','','','','과당','설탕','http://lampcook.com/wi_files/alcohol_gallery/item/item161.jpg',17,1),(24,'제주감귤주 귤로만(Jeju Citrus Wine, Gyulroman)','750ml',7.0,4.0,'Citrus juice (Jeju)','It is a fruit wine made with only tangerines not colored and flavored with tangerines and was named ‘tangerine manan’. It is a takju that is fermented with clean Jeju water using only 100% of Jeju tangerines grown in the clean air and fertile soil of Jeju.','','정제수','','','','','','','http://img.danawa.com/prod_img/500000/168/194/img/6194168_1.jpg?shrink=330:330&_v=20200708152517',15,5),(25,'산내울 오미자주(Sannaeul Omija Wine)','750ml',16.0,4.5,'Schisandra sugar alcohol purified water fructose','‘Sannaeul Omijaju’ produced by Geochang Apple Horticultural Agricultural Cooperatives in Geochang-gun Gyeongsangnam-do is a traditional liquor representing Geochang. The red color of omija is pleasing to the eye and the refreshing scent of omija and the five unique flavors of omija are harmonized to please the mouth.','','정제수','','','','주정','과당','','http://img.danawa.com/prod_img/500000/070/360/img/5360070_1.jpg?shrink=500:500&_v=20180906153350',16,3),(26,'백운복분자주(Baekun Raspberry Wine)','360ml',13.0,3.0,'Domestic rice Korean bokbunja','Baegun bokbunjaju is a traditional alcoholic beverage that is fermented at low temperature for a long time by steaming rice then adding yeast water and high sugar content of Gwangyang native bokbunja juice. There is no 